// Generated by kalamine on 2026-03-21
//
// This is a standalone XKB keymap file. To apply this keymap, use:
//   xkbcomp -w9 qwerty-l.xkb_keymap $DISPLAY
//
// DO NOT COPY THIS INTO xkb/symbols: THIS WOULD MESS UP YOUR XKB CONFIG.
//
// File          : qwerty-l.xkb_keymap
// Project page  : https://github.com/fabi1cazenave/qwerty-lafayette
// Author        : Fabien Cazenave (:kazГ©)
